> inventory status, sales velocity, and days to zero as this is currently all
> we are looking at.
> 2. This report would be a monthly report, preferably the 1st of each
> month, and dispersed to all departments.
> 3. This report is critical because it allows multiple departments to get a
> better understanding of what might be having a negative or positive impact
> on the sales of a particular product!
> 4. N/A
> 5. This report would be done by me solely. As I update our Master
